{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"blogTitle":"LaySent's Blog","author":"LaySent"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"0c92694b-cacd-5316-9186-d6ae10d88bed","html":"<p>一个好的 lint 工具，应该满足的条件：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>插件化\n提供各类插件，可以选择使用或不使用其中的部分，达到规则个性化的目的</li>\n<li>定制化\n类似于上一条，定制化在于对插件提供个性化的配置，规则不是写死的</li>\n</ol>\n<section><h2>JavaScript</h2></section>\n<section><h2>TypeScript</h2></section>\n<section><h2>CSS</h2></section>\n<section><h2>Markdown</h2></section>\n<section><h2>Git Commit</h2><p><a href=\"https://github.com/conventional-changelog/commitlint\">commitlint</a></p><section><h3>安装</h3><div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">npm install --save-dev @commitlint/config-conventional @commitlint/cli husky</code></pre></div><p>这里安装了三个部分，<a href=\"https://github.com/conventional-changelog/commitlint\"><code class=\"language-text\">commitlint</code></a> 用于检查 commit 信息；<a href=\"https://github.com/conventional-changelog/commitlint/tree/master/%40commitlint/config-conventional\"><code class=\"language-text\">@commitlint/config-conventional</code></a> 是 <code class=\"language-text\">commitlint</code> 的一份配置；<code class=\"language-text\">husky</code> 保证不同用户可以使用同一份 git 配置。</p><p>增加 <code class=\"language-text\">commitlint.config.js</code>，内容如下：</p><div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'@commitlint/config-conventional'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div><p><a href=\"https://conventional-changelog.github.io/commitlint/#/reference-rules\">Rules</a></p><p>在 <code class=\"language-text\">package.json</code> 里可以做如下配置：</p><div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"husky\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"hooks\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"commit-msg\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"commitlint -E HUSKY_GIT_PARAMS\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>  \n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div><p>关于 Conventional Commits，可以看<a href=\"https://www.conventionalcommits.org/en/v1.0.0-beta.3/\">这里</a></p></section></section>","frontmatter":{"title":"lint tools","date":"2019-03-08","modified":"2019-03-08","description":"这篇文章介绍各种常见的 Lint 工具"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/lint-tools/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Preload-Prefetch/","type":"draft"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Preload & Prefetch","category":"Tools","tags":"Tools"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/baseline-and-progressive-jpeg/","type":"blog"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Baseline & Progressive JPEG","category":"Web","tags":"Web, Graphics"}}}}